* 1912 — [[諾貝爾化學獎|諾貝爾化學獎]]
* 1912 — {{link-en|拉瓦錫獎章|Lavoisier Medal}},[[:en:Société_chimique_de_France|Société chimique de France]]<ref>Nobel Prize in Chemistry, 1912, [http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1912/grignard-bio.html Victor Grignard bio notes] {{Wayback|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1912/grignard-bio.html |date=20071012130436 }}</ref>
* 1933 — [[法國榮譽軍團勳章|法國榮譽軍團勳章]]<ref>Newbold, Brian T. [http://www.allbusiness.com/north-america/canada/826670-1.html  "Victor Grignard Ancestor of Organic Synthesis,"] ''Canadian Chemical News.'' October 1, 2001.</ref>

